d\Big(\frac{g'}{g^{\frac{3}{2}}}\Big)=\left(\frac{g''}{g^{\frac{3}{2}}}-\frac{3}{2}\cdot\frac{(g')^2}{g^{\frac{5}{2}}}\right)dx.
\tag{1}\int_Md\Big(\frac{g'}{g^{\frac{3}{2}}}\Big)=\int_M\left(\frac{g''}{g^{\frac{3}{2}}}-\frac{3}{2}\cdot\frac{(g')^2}{g^{\frac{5}{2}}}\right)dx.
\int_M\left(\frac{g''}{g^{\frac{3}{2}}}-\frac{(g')^2}{g^{\frac{5}{2}}}\right)dx=\int_M\frac{(g')^2}{g^{\frac{5}{2}}}dx.
